OL,6,FA man who shook a four-week-old baby
OL,7,Fleaving him bruised, blind, and brain
OL,8,Fdamaged has been jailed for 22 years.
OL,10,F35-year-old Christopher Fulton who
OL,11,Fattacked the little boy in 2019 was
OL,12,Ffound guilty in October.
OL,14,FHis ex-partner Amanda Fulton who is
OL,15,F36, was handed a four year sentence
OL,16,Ffor child cruelty by wilful neglect,
OL,17,Fwith half to be served in jail and
OL,18,Fhalf on licence.
